trans-unit.source: Animates from the <xref href="System.Windows.Thickness"></xref> value of the previous key frame to its own <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value*> using splined interpolation.
trans-unit.target: Animerer fra den <xref href="System.Windows.Thickness"> </xref> verdien for den forrige key rammen til sin egen <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value*>ved hjelp av splined interpolering.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value*>

trans-unit.source: This class is used as part of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrameCollection> in conjunction with a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to animate a <xref:System.Windows.Thickness> property value along a set of key frames.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes som en del av en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrameCollection>sammen med en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessAnimationUsingKeyFrames>å animere en <xref:System.Windows.Thickness>egenskapsverdien langs et sett med nøkkelen for forhandleren.</xref:System.Windows.Thickness> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessAnimationUsingKeyFrames> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrameCollection>

trans-unit.source: A key frame defines a segment of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to which it belongs.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en nøkkel for en del av den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessAnimationUsingKeyFrames>som den tilhører.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessAnimationUsingKeyFrames>

trans-unit.source: Each key frame has a target <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value%2A> and a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hver key ramme har et mål <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> specifies the time at which the key frame's <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value%2A> should be reached.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>angir tiden som nøkkelen rammens <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value%2A>kan nås.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ThicknessKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>

trans-unit.source: A key frame animates from the target value of the previous key frame to its own target value.
trans-unit.target: En nøkkel ramme animerer fra målverdien tidligere key rammens til verdien målet.

trans-unit.source: It starts when the previous key frame ends and ends when its own key time is reached.
trans-unit.target: Starter når den forrige key rammen slutter og slutter når sin egen key time er nådd.

trans-unit.source: Spline key frames like SplineThicknessKeyFrame creates a variable transition between values which is determined by the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame.KeySpline%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Spline nøkkelen rammer som SplineThicknessKeyFrame oppretter en variabel overgang mellom verdier som fastsettes av den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame.KeySpline%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame.KeySpline%2A>

trans-unit.source: Splined interpolation can be used to achieve more realistic "real world" timing effects such as acceleration and deceleration.
trans-unit.target: Splined interpolering kan brukes til å oppnå mer realistisk "reell" tidsberegning effekter for eksempel akselerasjon og deselerasjon.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"></xref> class with the specified ending value.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"> </xref> klasse angitte sluttverdien.

trans-unit.source: Ending value (also known as "target value") for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: SLUTTVERDI (også kjent som "målverdien") for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"></xref> class with the specified ending value and key time.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"> </xref> klassen med den angitte verdien og nøkkel sluttidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: Ending value (also known as "target value") for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: SLUTTVERDI (også kjent som "målverdien") for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: Key time for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: Key time for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: The key time determines when the target value is reached which is also when the key frame ends.
trans-unit.target: Key time bestemmer når målverdien er nådd som er også når key rammens slutter.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"></xref> class with the specified ending value, key time, and <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeySpline"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"> </xref> klasse med den angitte sluttverdien, nøkkel tid og <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeySpline"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Ending value (also known as "target value") for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: SLUTTVERDI (også kjent som "målverdien") for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: Key time for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: Key time for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: The key time determines when the target value is reached which is also when the key frame ends.
trans-unit.target: Key time bestemmer når målverdien er nådd som er også når key rammens slutter.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeySpline"></xref> for the key frame.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeySpline"></xref>for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeySpline"></xref> represents a Bezier curve which defines animation progress of the key frame.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.KeySpline"> </xref> representerer en Bezier kurve som definerer animasjonen fremdriften for nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineThicknessKeyFrame"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The new instance.
trans-unit.target: Den nye forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Uses splined interpolation to transition between the previous key frame value and the value of the current key frame.
trans-unit.target: Bruker splined interpolering overgang mellom forrige nøkkel for verdi og verdi for gjeldende key ramme.

trans-unit.source: The value to animate from.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for å animere fra.

trans-unit.source: A value between 0.0 and 1.0, inclusive, that specifies the percentage of time that has elapsed for this key frame.
trans-unit.target: En verdi mellom 0,0 og 1,0 med, som angir prosentdelen av tiden som er utløpt for denne nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: The output value of this key frame given the specified base value and progress.
trans-unit.target: Output-verdien for denne nøkkelen rammen gitt angitte grunnverdi og pågår.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the two control points that define animation progress for this key frame.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir to kontrollpunkt som definerer animasjonen fremdrift for denne nøkkelen rammen.

trans-unit.source: To understand how a KeySpline works, it is helpful to understand cubic Bezier curves.
trans-unit.target: For å forstå hvordan en KeySpline fungerer, er det nyttig å forstå cubic bezierkurver.

trans-unit.source: A cubic Bezier curve is defined by a start point, an end point, and two control points.
trans-unit.target: En cubic Bezier kurve er definert av et startpunkt, et sluttpunkt og to kontrollpunkt.

trans-unit.source: The two coordinates in the KeySpline defines those two control points.
trans-unit.target: To koordinater i KeySpline definerer disse to kontrollpunkt.

trans-unit.source: When describing key splines, the start point of the Bezier curve is always 0, and the end point is always 1, which is why you define only the two control points.
trans-unit.target: Når du beskriver key spline-kurver startpunktet Bezier kurve er alltid 0, og endepunktet er alltid 1, og derfor du definere bare to kontrollpunkt.

trans-unit.source: The resulting curve specifies how an animation is interpolated during a time segment; that is, the curve represents the rate of change in the animation's target attribute over the time segment.
trans-unit.target: Den resulterende kurven angir hvordan en animasjon interpoleres under en time-segmentet; Det vil si representerer buen endringsfrekvens i av animasjonen Målattributtet over tid segmentet.

trans-unit.source: To better see the relationship between animation progress and a Bezier curve, see [Key Spline Animation Sample](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=160011) .
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se bedre relasjonen mellom animasjonen pågår og en Bezier kurve, kan du se [nøkkelen Spline animasjonen utvalg](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=160011) .
